channel.title: Changing ports with delta base
channel.description:
Well I have a small problem. (for the note im not a noob that says things like "compileer dosnt work!!!!11", as I have coded my own server and have been around the block a bit with coding.) Anyway I need help with changing the login ports for my delta based server that I am developing, like most servers the port people log in with is in the server.JAVA file, but when I changed the ports in there it still stays as port 43594 being the default.
P.S.- yes I port fowarded and stuff so it will work with 43595. :D
